    <div class="fbcms_richtext_content">
        <p>Want to find out when the pool is closed?   There are times when we have no choice but to close our pool.  Whether it is inclement weather, maintenance, or a scheduling conflict, we want you to know when we will not be opening during our regularly scheduled hours. <a href="https://kentcityathletics.com/teams/2424685/swimming/kent-city-pool" target="_blank">Pool Closing Updates</a></p>

<p><a href="https://www.remind.com/" target="_blank"><img alt="" src="/downloads/_acct_/00/00/10/40/remind_logo.png" style="height:77px; width:304px"></a></p>

<p>Sign up for the Remind App: By giving us your cell phone number or email address, you will get notified by text/email anytime the pool will be closed. </p>

<ul>
<li>To sign up via cell phone enter 81010 and text this message: @kcpool. </li>
	<li>To sign up via email send an email kcpool@mail.remind.com</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>

<p> </p>

<p>  </p>
